WEBVTT

01:43.436 --> 01:45.396
Thought you were someone else.

01:46.147 --> 01:49.650
What a hideous face.
Don't think it can ever be fixed.

01:49.651 --> 01:51.402
What are you going to do, Maki?

01:52.445 --> 01:55.364
So, you can tell women apart
by their faces now?

01:55.365 --> 01:57.367
I thought you only ever looked
at their asses.

02:07.001 --> 02:10.755
I'm asking what you're going to do.
Answer me, you piece of trash.

02:11.798 --> 02:16.969
Can't use jujutsu or see cursed spirits.
Even that pretty face is ruined.

02:16.970 --> 02:20.098
No one even notices you anymore.

02:21.474 --> 02:23.351
How lonely.

02:23.852 --> 02:26.020
Should I bully you like I used to?

02:28.731 --> 02:30.274
So, what are you going to do?

02:30.275 --> 02:33.278
Just trailing behind Okkotsu
and Fushiguro like a goldfish turd?

02:36.114 --> 02:38.741
Say something, trash!

02:39.284 --> 02:40.702
<i>Maki, come back.</i>

02:42.203 --> 02:47.625
Did you forget?
We're not allowed to enter the armory.

02:48.751 --> 02:51.087
The clan head said it's fine.

02:52.505 --> 02:55.008
<i>Me, as the head of the Zen'in clan?</i>

02:56.175 --> 02:58.719
Yes. It's Naobito's will.

02:58.720 --> 03:00.971
I refuse. This is a hassle.

03:00.972 --> 03:02.891
Sorry, but you have to do it.

03:03.558 --> 03:08.270
Naobito said he would leave
all the Zen'in assets to you.

03:08.271 --> 03:13.443
Money, cursed tools… If you become head,
we'll get intel on the Big Three.

03:13.943 --> 03:16.695
It will change how we move from here on.

03:16.696 --> 03:20.032
Then Maki, you do it. I'll hand it to you.

03:20.033 --> 03:24.202
Right now, no one would accept me.
They wouldn't follow me.

03:24.203 --> 03:26.663
You've inherited the clan's technique.

03:26.664 --> 03:28.957
You've mastered a domain.

03:28.958 --> 03:32.629
And Satoru even had his eye on you.
You can handle this, though just barely!

03:34.756 --> 03:35.965
Who cares

03:36.633 --> 03:39.636
what the Zen'in clan thinks?

03:40.511 --> 03:44.098
You said I would get those benefits
as long as I'm clan head, right?

03:45.642 --> 03:48.061
But, I'm still not good enough.

03:50.605 --> 03:54.025
I can't create a place for Mai to belong.

03:58.404 --> 03:59.988
Understood.

03:59.989 --> 04:04.035
Come back!

04:08.873 --> 04:10.540
Why?

04:10.541 --> 04:13.878
Why are you always like this?

04:18.549 --> 04:21.760
Just once… Make me feel glad
I gave birth to you…

04:21.761 --> 04:23.096
Maki.

04:39.862 --> 04:40.989
Dad…

04:42.282 --> 04:45.325
If you were going to do this,
you should've said so from the start.

04:45.326 --> 04:47.953
You're rushing ahead too much.

04:47.954 --> 04:51.248
Sure, Megumi Fushiguro
is a little better than you.

04:51.249 --> 04:52.624
What?

04:52.625 --> 04:57.838
A lot of people want to support him
to repair ties with the Gojo clan.

04:57.839 --> 05:03.176
But we can't accept giving
every asset to Megumi Fushiguro.

05:03.177 --> 05:05.178
So, what were you hesitating over?

05:05.179 --> 05:09.683
Megumi Fushiguro has ties not only
to the Gojo clan,

05:09.684 --> 05:13.228
but also to the next head
of the Kamo clan, Noritoshi Kamo.

05:13.229 --> 05:17.399
If we erase him without reason,
the Zen'in clan loses standing.

05:17.400 --> 05:21.987
With Satoru Gojo sealed, we'll fall behind
in this shifting power struggle.

05:21.988 --> 05:24.531
Fine, I get that. But why now?

05:24.532 --> 05:27.285
You really haven't been listening
to the higher-ups' orders.

05:27.869 --> 05:29.578
We would be fools not to use it.

05:29.579 --> 05:34.124
As rebels who plotted to free Satoru Gojo,
we will execute

05:34.125 --> 05:36.294
Megumi Fushiguro, Maki, and Mai.

05:37.503 --> 05:41.256
Killing your own daughter
makes it more convincing, huh?

05:41.257 --> 05:45.719
Yes. And it will strengthen
the higher-ups' trust in us.

05:45.720 --> 05:49.473
<i>But is that really okay?
What about Uncle Ogi?</i>

05:49.474 --> 05:50.807
<i>It was Ogi's idea.</i>

05:50.808 --> 05:53.477
There are no cursed tools here, Maki.

05:53.478 --> 05:56.856
I anticipated your movements,
so I cleared it out.

06:00.568 --> 06:02.028
Why are you here,

06:03.071 --> 06:04.113
idiot?

06:11.245 --> 06:15.249
THE MASTERPIECE OF JUZO KUMIYA,
THE CURSED TOOL-DRAGON BONE

06:18.920 --> 06:21.631
SECRET TECHNIQUE-FALLING BLOSSOM EMOTION

06:22.215 --> 06:25.258
Do you know why I wasn't chosen
as the previous clan head,

06:25.259 --> 06:28.386
and my brother Naobito was?

06:28.387 --> 06:31.140
Because you're a piece of shit
who can kill kids.

06:46.405 --> 06:49.825
Do you know why
I couldn't become clan head?

06:49.826 --> 06:51.409
<i>Why?</i>

06:51.410 --> 06:54.412
- Because you brats…
<i>- It should've broken.</i>

06:54.413 --> 06:56.666
-…were failures.
<i>- The blade…</i>

07:08.136 --> 07:12.264
You broke the blade,
so you thought the distance had closed,

07:12.265 --> 07:16.436
and you stepped in deep.

07:17.061 --> 07:19.896
I'm not a swordsman, but a sorcerer.

07:19.897 --> 07:24.276
Trying to measure me
with a failure's standards is laughable.

07:24.277 --> 07:26.111
I'll say it as many times as it takes.

07:26.112 --> 07:30.366
The reason I wasn't chosen
as the previous clan head is you two.

07:30.908 --> 07:33.827
My brother's technique is young.

07:33.828 --> 07:37.581
Whether it counts as an inherited
clan technique wasn't the main issue.

07:37.582 --> 07:39.124
As a sorcerer,

07:39.125 --> 07:43.254
I never once fell behind my brother,
except for one thing.

07:44.005 --> 07:46.424
The quality of my children.

07:47.383 --> 07:49.426
Children dragging their parents down…

07:49.427 --> 07:51.679
That should never happen.

07:52.221 --> 07:57.226
You didn't know? In this country,
backstabbing is considered a virtue.

08:05.651 --> 08:09.279
This room is used for training
and punishment.

08:09.280 --> 08:12.073
I keep countless cursed spirits here.
Grade two and below.

08:12.074 --> 08:14.576
They fear me now,

08:14.577 --> 08:17.663
but soon, they'll come crawling out
to devour you.

08:18.831 --> 08:24.252
Heavenly Restriction, Physical Gifted.
So what?

08:24.253 --> 08:25.670
We sorcerers train every day,

08:25.671 --> 08:29.926
then reinforce our bodies
even further with cursed energy.

08:30.510 --> 08:31.927
Maki…

08:31.928 --> 08:36.432
Everyone here has that strength of yours,
without cutting corners.

08:37.808 --> 08:38.768
Farewell.

08:39.352 --> 08:41.604
You are a stain upon my life.

09:17.598 --> 09:18.641
As expected…

09:19.350 --> 09:20.643
You're persistent.

09:24.605 --> 09:25.856
I always thought

09:26.607 --> 09:29.443
this would happen someday.

09:44.417 --> 09:45.334
This is the worst.

10:12.695 --> 10:16.574
You know how my technique works
already, right?

10:17.283 --> 10:20.703
But I can't make big things,
or anything complicated.

10:24.498 --> 10:27.043
And I've got the wound
that man gave me too.

10:27.585 --> 10:30.963
If I make this, I'll die.

10:32.882 --> 10:34.549
From now on, just do your best.

10:34.550 --> 10:36.886
Hey, Mai! Wait!

10:38.179 --> 10:39.764
What are you saying?
Anyway, just come back!

10:41.641 --> 10:44.934
I've known for a long time

10:44.935 --> 10:48.230
why twins are considered
a bad omen for jujutsu sorcerers.

10:49.899 --> 10:53.151
To gain something,
you have to give something up.

10:53.152 --> 10:55.529
It's not just about binding vows.

10:56.197 --> 10:59.158
The logic is the same
as getting stronger through pain.

11:01.786 --> 11:05.455
That kind of trade-off

11:05.456 --> 11:06.791
doesn't properly work for twins.

11:08.417 --> 11:11.461
Because identical twins are treated

11:11.462 --> 11:14.548
as the same person in jujutsu.

11:15.257 --> 11:19.136
Get it? I'm you, and you're me.

11:19.678 --> 11:22.305
Even if you cough up blood, work hard,

11:22.306 --> 11:25.725
or wish to be strong,
it doesn't mean anything.

11:25.726 --> 11:28.562
Because I don't want to be strong.

11:30.231 --> 11:32.899
Even if you don't have a technique,

11:32.900 --> 11:35.360
if I do, then it's just the same.

11:35.361 --> 11:37.570
As long as I exist, Maki,

11:37.571 --> 11:39.364
you'll be half-baked forever.

11:39.365 --> 11:40.825
I get it!

11:41.867 --> 11:42.743
So just come back!

11:44.078 --> 11:47.081
I'll leave you this one thing.
Throw the rest away.

11:51.419 --> 11:53.378
Your cursed energy… everything.

11:53.379 --> 11:55.798
I'll take it with me.

11:56.882 --> 11:59.552
Just make me one promise.

12:01.429 --> 12:02.345
Destroy

12:02.346 --> 12:04.098
everything.

12:06.434 --> 12:07.977
Everything. Okay?

12:10.438 --> 12:11.772
<i>Big sister…</i>

12:18.237 --> 12:20.072
Mai!

12:20.656 --> 12:23.284
Mai! Wake up!

12:23.993 --> 12:26.704
Mai! Wake up!

12:27.329 --> 12:28.872
Mai!

12:28.873 --> 12:29.999
Wake up…

12:32.585 --> 12:33.419
Mai!

12:34.420 --> 12:35.463
Mai…

12:36.547 --> 12:38.048
Wake up…

12:39.467 --> 12:40.593
Mai…

12:41.469 --> 12:42.636
Wake up…

12:43.262 --> 12:44.263
Mai…

12:49.059 --> 12:51.228
A disappearance reaction
from a cursed spirit?

12:51.854 --> 12:52.979
What?

12:52.980 --> 12:54.398
My body remembers…

12:55.691 --> 12:59.278
The fear I tried so hard to forget…

13:01.655 --> 13:04.908
Technique Release. Blazing Courage!

13:04.909 --> 13:08.203
Fine then! One more time with these hands,

13:08.204 --> 13:10.748
I'll burn you to the marrow!

13:13.709 --> 13:16.212
Come! You failure!

13:27.306 --> 13:28.390
Mai.

13:29.725 --> 13:30.851
Let's begin.

13:49.411 --> 13:51.413
What the hell? So damn loud.

13:54.333 --> 13:58.211
Jinichi! Maki has gone berserk!
She has killed Mr. Ogi!

13:58.212 --> 14:00.964
The Kukuru Unit is handling it now!

14:00.965 --> 14:02.549
Even Ogi would slip up

14:02.550 --> 14:05.844
if he got ambushed in bed
or on the toilet.

14:06.428 --> 14:09.389
- Catch her before I get there.
- Yes, sir!

14:09.390 --> 14:13.727
If you screw around and Jinichi chews
me out, I, the captain, takes the heat.

14:14.228 --> 14:17.272
Hey. Don't kill her.
I'll finish her off myself.

14:17.273 --> 14:18.398
<i>The Kukuru Unit.</i>

14:18.399 --> 14:23.236
<i>Boys of the Zen'in clan who do not possess
cursed techniques are required to enlist.</i>

14:23.237 --> 14:27.031
<i>As a subordinate organization of Hei,
they're drilled in martial arts every day.</i>

14:27.032 --> 14:27.949
She's in Ton's room!

14:27.950 --> 14:28.950
<i>What will you do?</i>

14:28.951 --> 14:30.910
<i>I wonder what I was trying to do.</i>

14:30.911 --> 14:34.080
Two unidentified cursed tools
confirmed by sight.

14:34.081 --> 14:37.709
<i>Maki had belonged to the Kukuru Unit
until she enrolled at Jujutsu High.</i>

14:37.710 --> 14:39.586
<i>Why wouldn't</i>

14:39.587 --> 14:42.130
<i>you fall with me?</i>

14:42.131 --> 14:43.172
<i>Yes.</i>

14:43.173 --> 14:44.675
Surround her!

14:45.259 --> 14:46.676
<i>Maybe that</i>

14:46.677 --> 14:49.013
<i>was the right answer for us.</i>

14:50.222 --> 14:53.224
<i>Sorry… Sorry, Mai.</i>

14:53.225 --> 14:54.350
Surround her!

14:54.351 --> 14:55.269
<i>Promise me.</i>

14:56.770 --> 14:57.688
<i>Destroy</i>

14:58.355 --> 14:59.231
<i>everything.</i>

15:07.865 --> 15:09.283
<i>Everything. Okay?</i>

17:27.337 --> 17:29.423
Yo. How's it going?

17:30.591 --> 17:31.842
What?

17:32.426 --> 17:34.053
Well, I'll be damned…

18:01.955 --> 18:04.333
<i>Chojuro's technique…</i>

18:04.917 --> 18:07.210
<i>So Hei is here.</i>

18:07.211 --> 18:09.879
<i>Hei. A group made up of those</i>

18:09.880 --> 18:13.800
<i>recognized as Semi-Grade One or higher,
under Jujutsu High standards.</i>

18:13.801 --> 18:16.261
<i>The Zen'in clan's strongest unit
of sorcerers.</i>

18:30.692 --> 18:32.903
<i>She took Chojuro's hit,
so why can she still move?</i>

18:37.950 --> 18:40.786
<i>Even my cursed energy guard
was broken through, like it's nothing!</i>

18:43.705 --> 18:45.874
<i>Is this really Maki?</i>

19:01.890 --> 19:03.433
Jinichi!

19:03.934 --> 19:06.478
Hold her right there! Ranta!

19:16.780 --> 19:19.408
<i>I can't… hold her!</i>

19:23.328 --> 19:25.205
Don't hesitate, Jinichi!

19:25.914 --> 19:28.834
The Zen’in clan only still exists
because Toji chose not to wipe us out!

19:29.418 --> 19:33.880
You know it, right?
Maki has become the same as him!

19:33.881 --> 19:36.424
Now! Right here!

19:36.425 --> 19:39.178
Kill her!

20:07.664 --> 20:11.376
You did it… Jinichi…

20:27.601 --> 20:29.101
That's brutal.

20:29.102 --> 20:30.061
NAOYA ZEN’IN,
LEADER OF THE "HEI" UNIT

20:30.062 --> 20:32.481
Don't you have a heart?

20:34.566 --> 20:37.945
No. She took it with her.

20:38.946 --> 20:41.740
<i>I'm a genius, you know. Everyone says so.</i>

20:42.658 --> 20:44.868
<i>I'm next after Dad as head of the clan.</i>

20:47.454 --> 20:50.331
<i>And they say the Zen'in clan has a loser.</i>

20:50.332 --> 20:53.502
<i>A guy with not even
one millimeter of cursed energy.</i>

20:55.087 --> 20:57.130
<i>What kind of pathetic guy is he?</i>

21:00.175 --> 21:02.469
<i>What kind of miserable face does he have?</i>

21:07.641 --> 21:09.184
<i>Three, four, five, nine, ten, eleven.</i>

21:10.352 --> 21:11.436
<i>You…</i>

21:15.315 --> 21:16.149
<i>You…</i>

21:20.612 --> 21:21.863
<i>aren't Toji.</i>

21:24.408 --> 21:26.993
<i>The sin of the weak
is not knowing strength.</i>

21:26.994 --> 21:28.954
<i>No one ever understood Toji.</i>

21:31.832 --> 21:33.667
<i>Probably except Satoru.</i>

21:34.626 --> 21:39.256
<i>But you're not him.
The one who stands on that side is me!</i>

21:45.637 --> 21:46.679
<i>Projection Sorcery</i>

21:46.680 --> 21:48.306
- <i>This is bad!</i>
- <i>can't create movements</i>

21:48.307 --> 21:49.390
<i>that ignore physics</i>

21:49.391 --> 21:50.850
- <i>and trajectories too excessively.</i>
- Six, seven, eight.

21:50.851 --> 21:52.435
- <i>Likewise,</i>
- One, two, three, four.

21:52.436 --> 21:55.604
<i>its acceleration has a limit.</i>

21:55.605 --> 21:58.441
<i>But the more the technique is layered
without stopping,</i>

21:58.442 --> 22:00.776
<i>the faster it can become.</i>

22:00.777 --> 22:03.613
<i>The one who stands on that side is me!</i>

22:12.956 --> 22:14.248
<i>I won't stop now.</i>

22:14.249 --> 22:16.625
<i>I won't screw up like last time.</i>

22:16.626 --> 22:19.296
<i>Power is weight and speed!</i>

22:38.065 --> 22:40.192
<i>So it's a straight-up fight, huh?</i>

22:40.859 --> 22:42.068
I'll hold you close.

22:42.069 --> 22:44.571
<i>I'll blast straight through you
at top speed!</i>

22:49.034 --> 22:52.244
<i>Anything touched by the palm</i>

22:52.245 --> 22:55.581
<i>during Projection Sorcery must also move
within 1/24 of a second.</i>

22:55.582 --> 22:58.543
<i>If it fails to do so,
it will freeze for one second.</i>

23:03.256 --> 23:06.092
<i>You planned to take my hit</i>

23:06.093 --> 23:08.385
<i>even if your ribs shattered,
just to stop me, right?</i>

23:08.386 --> 23:11.097
<i>Like I would fall
for something that obvious!</i>

23:11.098 --> 23:13.058
<i>You really are a fake!</i>

23:18.230 --> 23:20.231
Twenty-four frames.

23:20.232 --> 23:24.611
You and Naobito weren't just fast.
Something felt off.

23:25.403 --> 23:28.115
You were slicing movement
into 24 beats every second.

23:28.615 --> 23:30.617
With this body, I can finally see it.

23:32.160 --> 23:33.787
You fake--

24:01.898 --> 24:03.024
Sorry.

24:03.733 --> 24:05.360
Say that one more time.

24:06.444 --> 24:07.737
Mom.

24:12.200 --> 24:13.368
Mom.

24:22.002 --> 24:24.044
- Mom.
- No!

24:24.045 --> 24:25.546
- Don't come near me!
- Mom.

24:25.547 --> 24:27.339
- Please. Listen.
- Why?

24:27.340 --> 24:29.341
Why are you…?

24:29.342 --> 24:32.679
Back then, why did you
tell me to "come back"?

24:35.974 --> 24:37.517
What are you talking about?

24:38.518 --> 24:44.149
No!

24:51.698 --> 24:54.993
Your finishing touch is sloppy,
you damn bitch!

25:06.588 --> 25:08.882
Don't screw with me!

25:09.549 --> 25:11.675
<i>I can't even mold cursed energy…</i>

25:11.676 --> 25:14.346
Damn trash!

25:20.644 --> 25:23.480
<i>I'm glad I gave birth to you…</i>

25:28.318 --> 25:29.736
Mai!

25:36.618 --> 25:40.455
That's why… I… Don't go…

25:43.917 --> 25:46.336
I'll leave the rest to you.

25:47.963 --> 25:50.340
What are you going to do now, Maki?

25:53.009 --> 25:55.052
SIX MEMBERS OF "HEI,"
NINE MEMBERS OF "SHO,"

25:55.053 --> 25:57.471
AND 21 FROM THE KUKURU UNIT

25:57.472 --> 25:59.765
MET THEIR TRAGIC DEATHS SOON AFTER

25:59.766 --> 26:01.684
NO RESIDUALS WERE FOUND,
BUT SOME CURSED ENERGY

26:01.685 --> 26:03.727
FROM THE CURSED MURDER WEAPON

26:03.728 --> 26:05.896
WAS DETECTED IN THE VICTIMS' WOUNDS.

26:05.897 --> 26:07.815
LATER, THE GOJO AND KAMO CLAN
SENT A PROPOSAL

26:07.816 --> 26:10.025
TO THE HIGHER-UPS
TO REMOVE THE ZEN'IN CLAN

26:10.026 --> 26:11.820
FROM THE BIG THREE FAMILIES.
THE PROPOSAL IS ON HOLD.

27:51.836 --> 27:54.004
<i>Hakari argued with the higher-ups
and got suspended.</i>

27:54.005 --> 27:55.714
- <i>Gambling matches?</i>
- <i>Don't you ever</i>

27:55.715 --> 27:57.925
- <i>mention gambling matches.
- The distance just won't close.</i>

27:57.926 --> 28:00.010
<i>Itadori will investigate from the inside.</i>

28:00.011 --> 28:02.096
<i>I love Kinji when he's fired up.</i>

28:02.097 --> 28:04.849
<i>Want to get swept up in my "heat"?</i>
